stimulus:
Welcome to the experiment

This experiment is designed to test your perceptual word learning boundaries. By clicking the option below you consent to participate in the expeirment.

Observation Instructions

You will observe three objects being named several times. Just sit back and watch.

Production Instructions

Next, you will be shown the same objects again. Please name these objects like you saw in the observation stage. This will repeat several times.

Perception Instructions

You will be shown the same objects again. Please rate how often in the Observation Phase you saw each object lable in proportion to each other. you can do this by sliding the slider so it matches the ratio of words you observed for each object in the Observation Phase

Finished!

Thanks for taking part in our expeirment!

Click Continue to finish the experiment and see your raw data. Please notify a team member when the raw data is shown on screen.
